br />\n廣州市社會科學院高級研究員彭澎認為，內地近年結婚率下降，年輕人婚戀觀念也受媒體影響而不太健康，如果政府可以提供具規範化的教育和諮詢服務，相信有助改善問題，但建議研究學校教材及諮詢服務時，應該以指引導向為原則，以免過份干預年輕人的選擇自由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"點樣教？因黨之名，依家你兩個L樣要結婚？因黨之名，你依家係某幹部後宮？on9"},{"pid":"6b499d3cf1d37423dffefb4655b79440f557e29d","tid":2494934,"uid":265338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"139621bc89fedfb75e108490b0a77f40fd8655b8","tid":2494934,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9fee339aa3b9efb43a961ced9aa0ba0d59667682","tid":2494934,"uid":84783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd78feca4348def07b26ad64cbb798409ea28511","tid":2494934,"uid":321345,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"支那男多女少 應該連美極都唔夠分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"鬼叫咁多棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"可能遲啲強制1男娶2女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多女？4男分一個老婆就差唔多"},{"pid":"12a237dcce3e6421a4b10111be2807b1dad76c22","tid":2494934,"uid":5695,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"22a52c273cf3d891265c807fbe44379fead52e0c","tid":2494934,"uid":321345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"254e3d365050d18fd92f403fa526319a32f94c00","tid":2494934,"uid":5695,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"搞咁多嘢不如放多啲後生支那妹落嚟好過啦 日日百五個成堆阿叔阿嬸生育率唔低都奇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"支那人不了<br />\n你自己去支那食到夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"依家啲支那妹好高質㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚟得香港讀書個班有返咁上下家